                            you yet you need your space; you need that person to respect your thoughts
                            and let you do things on your own course yet you want that person to offer
                            their unsolicited views, and I could go on and on about how this universal
                            feeling called "LOVE" is so unfathomable and complex. Perhaps, this is why,
                            no matter how many movies are made around the central theme of love, new
                            ones with fresher perspective like "Lover" still are celebrated by the audience.
